		<slide showAnimation="ScaleFromMax" hideAnimation="FadeOut">

			<title>Service Layer</title>

			<content name="Principle">
				<title>Principle</title>

				<item>Services are JRebirth Components</item>
				<item></item>
				<item>Services are used to handle long task</item>
				<item level="1">with asynchronous callback</item>
				<item level="1">with or without any state</item>
				<item></item>
				<item>A service is composed by one</item>
				<item>or several ServiceTask</item>
			</content>

			<content name="Running">
				<title>Threading</title>

				<item>Each ServiceTask is called into JTP</item>
				<item level="1">or HPTP according to their priority</item>
				<item level="1">Defined by @Priority</item>
				<item>The result is wrapped into a Wave</item>
				<item level="1">that can be processed in any thread (JAT, JIT, JTP)</item>
				<item level="1">that can be omitted when returning void</item>
				<item>Allow following Task progression</item>
				<item level="1">update progress bar into JAT</item>
				<item level="1">update message into JAT</item>
				<item></item>
				<item>A ServiceTask is created in 4 steps</item>
			</content>


